---
import PageLayout from '../../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Coaching | Académie Évolution"
  description="Simple, structured coaching for men who want lasting results."
  lang="en"
>
  <section class="relative z-20 flex min-h-[50vh] items-end border-0">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 w-full">
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl sm:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-[.9] anim-slide-l" style="--delay:.35s">
        Simple coaching.<br />Lasting results.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/65 leading-relaxed mt-6 max-w-2xl anim-fade-up" style="--delay:.5s">
        Built for busy dads and men who want to lose fat, regain energy, and build consistency.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 anim-fade-up" style="--delay:.65s">
        <a href="/en/signin/" class="btn btn-primary">Free consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="relative z-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mb-10 reveal" style="--delay:.1s">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">The real problem.</h2>
        <p class="text-white/65 mt-3 max-w-2xl">You don’t yet have a simple structure that fits your reality.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 reveal" style="--delay:.1s">
          <p class="font-display font-semibold tracking-tight text-lg">You’re short on time</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 mt-2">Your week fills up and training ends up last on the list.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 reveal" style="--delay:.2s">
          <p class="font-display font-semibold tracking-tight text-lg">You keep restarting</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 mt-2">You start motivated, hold on for a bit, then life catches up.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 reveal" style="--delay:.3s">
          <p class="font-display font-semibold tracking-tight text-lg">You want something concrete</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 mt-2">But not an extreme method you can’t sustain.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="relative z-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mb-10 reveal" style="--delay:.1s">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">The solution.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/[.15] transition-colors reveal" style="--delay:.1s">
          <p class="font-display text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Training plan that fits</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/65 mt-3">Based on your level, schedule, and constraints.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/[.15] transition-colors reveal" style="--delay:.2s">
          <p class="font-display text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Realistic nutrition structure</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/65 mt-3">Lose fat without turning life into a prison.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/[.15] transition-colors reveal" style="--delay:.3s">
          <p class="font-display text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Guidance</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/65 mt-3">Know what to do, what to adjust, and how to keep going.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/[.15] transition-colors reveal" style="--delay:.4s">
          <p class="font-display text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Accountability</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/65 mt-3">Staying consistent alone isn’t always realistic.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/[.15] transition-colors reveal" style="--delay:.5s">
          <p class="font-display text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Measurable progress</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/65 mt-3">You know where you’re headed and how to track wins.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/[.15] transition-colors reveal" style="--delay:.6s">
          <p class="font-display text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Support</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/65 mt-3">Clear frequency and adjustments when the week gets heavy.</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center mt-10 reveal" style="--delay:.6s">
        <a href="/en/signin/" class="btn btn-primary">Free consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
